<article id="post-1464" class="post-1464 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-costa-rica category-family category-general category-travel tag-alajuela tag-birthday tag-butterflies tag-hotels tag-volcanoes tag-weather">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/07/a-wet-birthday-vacation/" rel="bookmark">A (wet) birthday vacation</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Well, Monkey, if your memory is any good, you should remember the last few days for the rest of your life. And not because you got to spend five uninterrupted days with your dad (remember, <a href="http://www.sowrey.org/2009/07/im-not-old/">I just turned 37</a> &#8230; I&#8217;m not old), or even because Nana is here for a visit.<br />
It&#8217;s &#8216;cuz I doubt you&#8217;ll ever see that much rain ever again.<br />
