<article id="post-1462" class="post-1462 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-pop-culture category-technology tag-science">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/07/forty-years-from-one-step/" rel="bookmark">Forty years from one step</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Like almost everyone in my generation (who isn&#8217;t more than three years older than me) has lived in a world where humans have set foot on the moon. For us, this isn&#8217;t just an historical event &#8212; it&#8217;s a part of our culture. Almost everyone knows the phrase:</p>
<blockquote><p>That&#8217;s one small step for [a] man, one giant leap for mankind.</p></blockquote>
<p>It&#8217;s more than a line from a movie. It&#8217;s more than a scene from a newsreel. It&#8217;s more than a footnote from a history textbook. It&#8217;s the moment when the sheer power of human will and imagination proved that the impossible is not beyond reach.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/07/forty-years-from-one-step/#more-1462" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Forty years from one step&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/07/forty-years-from-one-step/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2009-07-15T22:29:45-06:00">15 July 2009</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/pop-culture/" rel="category tag">Pop Culture</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/technology/" rel="category tag">Technology</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/science/" rel="tag">science</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/07/forty-years-from-one-step/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Forty years from one step</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
</article><!-- #post-1462 -->

<article id="post-1458" class="post-1458 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-costa-rica category-general tag-amusement tag-parks tag-san-jose">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/07/diversions-at-parque-diversiones/" rel="bookmark">Diversions at Parque Diversiones</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Well, Kiddo, today was a really fun day!<br />
Plans don&#8217;t always go according to plan, but there are those times when one plan ends up giving who new plans that are possibly even more fun than the original ones. I&#8217;d like to think today was like that, largely because we got to go somewhere fun, and I got to spend nearly the whole day with you! (Except for, y&#8217;know, when you were sleeping.)<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/07/diversions-at-parque-diversiones/#more-1458" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Diversions at Parque Diversiones&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/07/diversions-at-parque-diversiones/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2009-07-11T22:45:13-06:00">11 July 2009</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/costa-rica/" rel="category tag">Costa Rica</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/amusement/" rel="tag">amusement</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/parks/" rel="tag">parks</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/san-jose/" rel="tag">san jose</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/07/diversions-at-parque-diversiones/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Diversions at Parque Diversiones</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
